===INTRODUCTION===
The files that are contained in this folder (../spec/*)
are the step files that run the actual tests.

They pull their class definitions from the ../lib/ directory,
and their configuration files from the ../fixtures directory.

Any modifications to the data being inputted must be done through
the test's respective config/YAML file.

===HOW TO RUN TESTS===
All test are run via their spec file via the command:

rspec -c -fd <test_name_here>
